        "title": "Setting a character limit for a string using Java annotations",
        "body": "<p>I'm trying to create a string with a character length restriction of 12 for my JBOSS Seam project. The string must either be 12 characters or blank. My length annotation is correct which is the following:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>    @Length(min = 12,max = 12)\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>However when I try to put a null value in there I get an InvalidStateException: validation fail error. Any ideas how to allow this?  <\/p>\n",
