            "creation_date": 1372866479,
            "body": "<p>Null value for String and empty String are not the same thing.  You are passing a null value (not a String of length 0).  Check this out:<\/p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/4802015/difference-between-null-and-java-string\">Difference between null and empty (&quot;&quot;) Java String<\/a><\/p>\n\n<p>Also, you should try out @Size(min=,max=).<\/p>\n",
